Title: Marrakech Intense
Author: gamut-director

EXT. MARRAKECH ROOFTOP - GOLDEN HOUR

A breeze pushes dust across the tiled rooftop. The medina hums in the distance, the city is rust-colored against a fading sky.

CUT TO:

INT. SOUK CORRIDOR - DAY

Light shafts through a wooden lattice. Cardamom pods, dried neroli, and crumbled sandalwood rest in shallow brass dishes. A hand passes across the spices.

CUT TO:

INT. TANNERY COURTYARD - LATE AFTERNOON

Stacked leathers in saffron, ochre, oxblood. Steam drifts from a copper vat. The colors saturate as the camera drifts closer.

CUT TO:

EXT. ARCHED ALLEY - DUSK

A still, narrow alley framed by terracotta walls. A single doorway sits at the vanishing point. The city quiets.

FADE OUT.
